From the Infowars web site ::

Alex covers the mid-term election and its results including the win of Rand Paul in Kentucky and the ascension of the Tea Party. 


Alex talks with Mancow Muller [2nd half of hour 1], host of Mancow's Morning Madhouse, a nationally syndicated talk radio show. Alex covers other news and takes calls on the issues.
